events.title: FBINET to UNET File Upload
events.description: An email was sent from an FBI address indicating that files were uploaded to UNET, including a case evidence report from New York.

keyFacts: An email was sent on March 15, 2021, regarding the upload of files from FBINET to UNET.
The email includes an attachment named 'Case_Evidence_Report-20210315-1809_-_NY.xlsx', suggesting it contains case evidence related to New York.
The document is identified as EFTA00154689, indicating it is part of the Epstein case evidence records.
